+
+#. Type: note
+#. Description
+#: ../dbconfig-common.templates:34001
+msgid "PostgreSQL connection method error"
+msgstr "PostgreSQL への接続方法のエラー"
+
+#. Type: note
+#. Description
+#: ../dbconfig-common.templates:34001
+msgid ""
+"Unfortunately, it seems that the database connection method you have "
